{"id":321062,"type":1,"name":"むすぶと本。","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/1f/46/321062_9IDL4.jpg","summary":"本は読み手を、深く愛している。\r\n本の声が聞こえる少年・榎木むすぶ。とある駅の貸本コーナーで出会った1冊の児童書は“ハナちゃんのところに帰らないと”と切羽詰まった声で訴えていた。恋人の夜長姫(=本)に激しく嫉妬され、学園の王子様・姫倉先輩の依頼を解決しながら、“ハナちゃん”を探し当てるのだけれど……。健気な本たちの想いを、むすぶは叶えることができるのか!? 泉鏡花の『外科室』ほか、“本の味方!”榎木むすぶがさまざまな人と本の問題を解決する学園ビブリオミステリー登場!","info":"<li><span>作者: </span><a href=\"/person/6023\">野村美月</a></li><li><span>插图: </span><a href=\"/person/5839\">竹岡美穂</a></li><li><span>出版社: </span><a href=\"/person/19306\">KADOKAWA</a></li><li><span>开始: </span>2020-06-30</li><li><span>特设页面: </span>https://famitsubunko.jp/special/musubutohon/entry-12676.html</li>","collection":{"wish":5,"collect":1,"doing":3},"tags":[{"name":"2020","count":1},{"name":"日本轻小说","count":1},{"name":"野村美月","count":1}],"crt":[{"id":87776,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/d0/34/87776_crt_hZjvd.jpg","name":"榎木むすぶ","desc":"主角"},{"id":87777,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/6a/09/87777_crt_15656.jpg","name":"夜长姬","desc":"主角"},{"id":87778,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/83/d0/87778_crt_U89Au.jpg","name":"妻科早苗","desc":"配角"},{"id":87779,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/21/f1/87779_crt_501h0.jpg","name":"姬仓悠人","desc":"配角"},{"id":87780,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/07/88/87780_crt_F09l0.jpg","name":"姬仓萤","desc":"配角"},{"id":87781,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/84/19/87781_crt_5QX5x.jpg","name":"若迫高也","desc":"配角"}],"staff":[{"id":6023,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/f1/d6/6023_prsn_leteA.jpg","name":"野村美月","desc":"作者"},{"id":5839,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/03/70/5839_prsn_w7pPZ.jpg","name":"竹冈美穗","desc":"插图"},{"id":19306,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/1c/1f/19306_prsn_x413b.jpg","name":"角川","desc":"出版社"}],"relations":[{"id":309645,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/32/e1/309645_4Juzk.jpg","title":"むすぶと本。 『さいごの本やさん』の長い長い終わり","type":"番外篇","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/309645"},{"id":499,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/3c/f1/499_QyAUf.jpg","title":"文学少女","type":"相同世界观","url":"https://bgm.tv/subje